(2)
A further view soutnward to East 50th (Uunscomb Place) Street. Katherine Cornell, William S. Paley, Abram Poole, Merrill Bmith and Mrs. Ellen Shipman reside
in the block shown.
The distinctive 37 story building, (No. 33, the former Jackson E. Reynolds home) has been sold to Billy RoSe, showmian. An account of this app3eared in the New
York Times of Decemoer 28, 1939.
September 20, 1927
P. L. Sperr
